            </para>
         </proof.block.body>
      </proof.block>
      <proof.block>
         <logic>
            <part.ref>AddVector</part.ref>
         </logic>
         <caption>AddVector</caption>
         <proof.block.body>
            <para>
               <para.body>Let <math>
                     <latex>T:=S\cup \Set{ \Vect{b} }</latex>
                  </math>. We show first that linear independence of <math>
